Get away from him!

542
00:49:09,207 --> 00:49:10,409
Get the hell away from my son!

543
00:49:10,410 --> 00:49:11,442
Jakie!

544
00:49:11,842 --> 00:49:13,213
Jakie!

545
00:49:15,648 --> 00:49:16,912
Jakie. Come here.

546
00:49:16,913 --> 00:49:18,614
Come here. Jakie.

547
00:49:19,652 --> 00:49:20,720
Jakie!

548
00:49:51,320 --> 00:49:55,650
What's happening to you
both is very normal.

