00:50:00,290 --> 00:50:03,628
one that brings up
all kinds of issues.

551
00:50:03,629 --> 00:50:04,629
Such as?

552
00:50:05,228 --> 00:50:06,628
Such as,

553
00:50:06,629 --> 00:50:10,204
"How will I ever let my
