554
00:50:10,868 --> 00:50:12,467
Or...

555
00:50:12,468 --> 00:50:15,671
"Did I fulfill my
obligation as a husband

556
00:50:16,614 --> 00:50:20,044
"and a father, and a man,

557
00:50:20,045 --> 00:50:21,677
"to protect my
wife and child?"

558
00:50:23,181 --> 00:50:25,953
Karina, Pat's description.

559
00:50:25,954 --> 00:50:28,988
It's quite evocative
of a persistent phobia

560
00:50:28,989 --> 00:50:31,027
your husband struggled
